public class MinExtension<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends GSpanEdge<NodeType,EdgeType>

Represents a possible extension used during the test for beingcanonical.

It can/will be stored in local object pool to avoid object generation/garbage collection.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
